Title: JET Range Condensate FP3380 tank pump - ACR - 1.7ltr
Description: JET ACR condensate pump offers both high performance and efficiency in a compact, space saving design. Specifically engineered to the requirements on AC units, this pump collects excess condensate water that is produced and discharges it safely up to a maximum head height of 5m. The JET ACR condensate pump also features a non-return valve, a pre-wired safety switch, plug and play connectivity, making it the perfect go to choice for those installations that require a high performing, easy to install and maintain condensate pump.

Title: Grundfos Conlift 1 LS Conlift1 LS condensate pump pack
Description: The one phase Grundfos Conlift1 LS condensate pump is used to lift condensate collected below sewer level. This 230V 50Hz pump can also be used in situations where condensate is unable to flow to a sewage system or drain via a natural downward slope.

Title: Grundfos Conlift 1 LS Conlift 1 Ls Condensate Pump
Description: Suitable for condensate boiler or air conditioner use, the Grundfos Conlift1 0.075kW condensate removal pump removes the condensate that collects below sewer level or that which can't flow to the building's sewage system or drain via a natural downward slope. This pump is compatible with condensate with a pH value above 2.5.

Title: Pump House unvented cylinder temperature and pressure pump
Description: The UK-built Pump House heavy duty temperature and pressure relief pump is a high temperature tank pump offering reliable thermal overload protection and a high level alarm switch. With a discharge rate of 32 LPM, this pump is suitable for unvented cylinder T&P discharge and steam humidifiers. It can withstand high flow rates as well as high temperatures of up to 100°C.

Title: Pump House pressure relief valve and condensate hot water pump 3.8ltr
Description: Suitable for condensate and PRV discharge in boilers up to 42kW and boiler only up to 600kW, this Pump House 3.8L pressure relief and boiler condensate pump can withstand over 100° when both pressure and temperature in the boiler are released, thanks to its high temperature plastic construction and high spec hose. Handling standard condensate, this pump will instantly reduce the temperature of any PRV discharge and has an extra-large drink cycle of 1.5L.

Title: Grundfos Conlift 1 1 phase condensate pump
Description: Designed for use with an air conditioning system or a condensing boiler, the Grundfos Conlift1 0.075kW condensate removal pump is able to remove any condensate that collects below sewer level or where the lack of a downward slope means that it isn't able to naturally flow into a sewage system. Offering entirely automatic operation, this pump is suitable for use with condensate of 2.5pH or higher.
